topic.body:
Hi! I integrated the anonymoose's TORv3 patch in my branch and keep working on other features:

https://github.com/zeronet-enhanced/ZeroNet/commits/massive-rework
https://github.com/zeronet-enhanced/ZeroHello/commits/master

I'm digging ConnectionServer and FileServer implementation attempting to improve the networking facilities. Anyone now working on other forks? We can join forces and prepare the next ZN release together.

Any actual patches, pull reqs etc?

@styromaniac
@zeroseed
@anonymoose

