1584763992_1CpcxT1xWtqTRZTRR1KnH8gGsY2i4.body:
> [sdfsdgasdew](#comment_18_1CpcxT1xWtqTRZTRR1KnH8gGsY2i4rJ7du): Yes , I modified the right file

No, you didn't.

The icons are embedded into css.

This way:

```
.icon-topic-chat {
	width: 48px; height: 48px;
	background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);
}
```

You have to modify css.

> [gitcenter](#comment_1340_1Cy3ntkN2GN9MH6EaW6eHpi4YoRS2nK5Di): Wait... does this mean one icon is embedded and another one isn't?


The only non-embedded icon seem to be `img/loading.gif`.

